                </nav>
                <main class="col-8 maincontainer ctr">
                    <img class="mx-auto d-block mb-4" src="/images/graveyard/linebreak.png">
                    <section class="text-center mb-4">
                        <p><em>What Comes Next?</em> is a dark fantasy, D&amp;D 5E campaign I run for my school with a focus on psychological horror, surrealism and, of course, mortality. The campaign itself is a homebrew setting within the afterlife, with heavy inspiration from Forgotten Realms.</p>
                        <p>The purpose of this page is to archive our sessions in a more permanent format than a Discord thread, as well as a wiki for my players to access important worldbuilding info as they discover it!</p>
                    </section>
                    <article class="infoscroll">
                        <h2>Last Session</h2>
                        <hr>
                        <h4> Forest's Lament - <span id="wcn1x3">14 months ago</span> <span class="float-right">(11/03/23)</span></h4>
                        <p>As the group heads deeper into the woods in search of the lost child, Douglas notices an oddly familiar shadow following them around. Only he can understand its words as it begs for help...</p>
